title: A Master Class in Playing Jazz with Saxophonist Benny Golson: Pre-Show Interview with Students
fulltitle: A Master Class in Playing Jazz with Saxophonist Benny Golson: Pre-Show Interview with Students
description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Saxophonist Benny Golson takes questions from jazz students at Loyola University, New Orleans, as part of a master class in playing jazz.
